Verses.Text:
 Jehovah has become like an enemy;
He has swallowed down Israel.
He has swallowed down all her towers;
He has destroyed all its fortified places.
And in the daughter of Judah he makes mourning and lamentation abound.
ו [Waw]

 As if for a festival day, you summon terrors from every direction.
In the day of the wrath of Jehovah, no one escaped or survived;
Those whom I gave birth to and reared, my enemy exterminated.

 He has blocked up my paths with hewn stones;
He has made my roadways crooked.
ד [Daleth]
